trans-unit.source: IMG_ARC_PIE and IMG_ARC_CHORD are mutually exclusive; IMG_ARC_CHORD just connects the starting and ending angles with a straight line, while IMG_ARC_PIE produces a rounded edge. IMG_ARC_NOFILL indicates that the arc or chord should be outlined, not filled. IMG_ARC_EDGED, used together with IMG_ARC_NOFILL, indicates that the beginning and ending angles should be connected to the center - this is a good way to outline (rather than fill) a 'pie slice'.
trans-unit.target: IMG_ARC_PIE 和 IMG_ARC_CHORD 是互斥的； IMG_ARC_CHORD 仅将起点和终点角度与一条直线相连，而 IMG_ARC_PIE 则产生一个圆角。 IMG_ARC_NOFILL 指示应勾勒弧线或和弦，而不要填充。 IMG_ARC_EDGED ，再加上使用 IMG_ARC_NOFILL ，预示着开始和结束的角度应连接到中心-这是纲要（而不是填充）一个“饼片”的好办法。

trans-unit.source: IMG_BICUBIC_FIXED: Fixed point implementation of the bicubic interpolation.

trans-unit.source: IMG_BILINEAR_FIXED: Fixed point implementation of the bilinear interpolation (default (also on image creation)).
trans-unit.target: IMG_BILINEAR_FIXED ：双线性插值的定点实现（默认（同样在图像创建时））。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_BRIGHTNESS: Changes the brightness of the image. Use arg1 to set the level of brightness. The range for the brightness is -255 to 255.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_BRIGHTNESS ：更改图像的亮度。使用 arg1 设置亮度等级。亮度范围是-255至255。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_COLORIZE: Alpha channel, A value between 0 and 127. 0 indicates completely opaque while 127 indicates completely transparent.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_COLORIZE ：Alpha通道，介于0和127之间的值。0表示完全不透明，而127表示完全透明。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_COLORIZE: Like IMG_FILTER_GRAYSCALE, except you can specify the color. Use arg1, arg2 and arg3 in the form of red, green, blue and arg4 for the alpha channel. The range for each color is 0 to 255.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_COLORIZE ：与 IMG_FILTER_GRAYSCALE 一样，除了可以指定颜色。将 arg1 ， arg2 和 arg3 以 red ， green ， blue 和 arg4 的形式用于 alpha 通道。每种颜色的范围是0到255。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_CONTRAST: Changes the contrast of the image. Use arg1 to set the level of contrast.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_CONTRAST ：更改图像的对比度。使用 arg1 设置对比度级别。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_EDGEDETECT: Uses edge detection to highlight the edges in the image.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_EDGEDETECT ：使用边缘检测来突出显示图像中的边缘。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_GAUSSIAN_BLUR: Blurs the image using the Gaussian method.

IMG_FILTER_GRAYSCALE: Converts the image into grayscale by changing the red, green and blue components to their weighted sum using the same coefficients as the REC.601 luma (Y') calculation. The alpha components are retained. For palette images the result may differ due to palette limitations.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_GRAYSCALE ：使用与REC.601亮度（Y'）计算相同的系数，通过将红色，绿色和蓝色分量更改为其权重和，将图像转换为灰度。保留了alpha分量。对于调色板图像，由于调色板限制，结果可能有所不同。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_MEAN_REMOVAL: Uses mean removal to achieve a "sketchy" effect.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_MEAN_REMOVAL ：使用均值消除来实现“粗糙 ”效果。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_NEGATE: Reverses all colors of the image.

trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_PIXELATE ：对图像应用像素化效果，使用 arg1 设置块大小，使用 arg2 设置像素化效果模式。

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_PIXELATE: Whether to use advanced pixelation effect or not (defaults to FALSE).

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_SCATTER: Effect substraction level. This must not be higher or equal to the addition level set with arg2.

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_SCATTER: Optional array indexed color values to apply effect at.

trans-unit.source: IMG_FILTER_SMOOTH: Makes the image smoother. Use arg1 to set the level of smoothness.
trans-unit.target: IMG_FILTER_SMOOTH ：使图像更平滑。使用 arg1 设置平滑度。
IMG_GENERALIZED_CUBIC ：广义三次样条曲线分形插值。

trans-unit.source: LDAP_OPT_SERVER_CONTROLS and LDAP_OPT_CLIENT_CONTROLS require a list of controls, this means that the value must be an array of controls. A control consists of an oid identifying the control, an optional value, and an optional flag for criticality. In PHP a control is given by an array containing an element with the key oid and string value, and two optional elements. The optional elements are key value with string value and key iscritical with boolean value. iscritical defaults to FALSE if not supplied. See » draft-ietf-ldapext-ldap-c-api-xx.txt for details. See also the second example below.

trans-unit.source: MYSQLI_TRANS_START_WITH_CONSISTENT_SNAPSHOT: Start the transaction as "START TRANSACTION WITH CONSISTENT SNAPSHOT".
trans-unit.target: MYSQLI_TRANS_START_WITH_CONSISTENT_SNAPSHOT ：以“ START CONSISTENT SNAPSHOT开始交易”来启动事务。
